name: Lace Closure
description:
-Our Lace Closure are the final piece to complement a Wavy, curly or straight Extension installation. 
-This closure can be parted in any direction,without being permanent. 
-Our closures contain baby hair in the front so that it looks more like your natural hairline. 
-They are also very easy to style and maintain, just like your hair extension weave.
